@baseUrl = http://localhost:8002
@productId = 42
@from = 2024-03-01
@to = 2024-03-14

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/status HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

### Cache metrics (confirm cache-only mode and index counts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/cache/metrics HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

### Product availability (valid)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rentals/products/{{productId}}/availability?from={{from}}&to={{to}} HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

### Product availability (invalid date format -> 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rentals/products/{{productId}}/availability?from=2024-03-40&to=2024-03-14 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

### Product availability (from > to -> 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rentals/products/{{productId}}/availability?from=2024-03-15&to=2024-03-14 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

###

### Product availability (missing params -> 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rentals/products/{{productId}}/availability HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
